            "id": "s_l1_3",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Creating Variables ✨",
            "content": "To create a variable, use the `let` keyword followed by a name.\n\n`let myName = 'Alice';`\n\nHere, `myName` is the label, and `'Alice'` is the value inside.",
            "codeSnippet": "let score = 100;\nconsole.log(score);",
            "codeLanguage": "javascript",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
