            "id": "s_l1_4",
            "type": "tip",
            "title": "The Old Way 👴",
            "content": "## Avoid using `var`\n\nYou might see `var` in older code. It's the old way of making variables.\n\nModern JavaScript uses `let` and `const` because they are safer and less confusing."
